Lasse_Kl In vlc, to open the subtitle file, play the video file first and then right click on the screen and go to subtitle and open the subtitle file. That's it.

If the names of the video file and sub file are different, Copy the video file name and erase the sub file name without the extension i.e. .srt, and then paste it. Therefore, subtitle will play automatically.
